# Never commit generated NM connection files (they hold UUIDs and may hold
# Wi-Fi PSKs). Only the .example templates belong in the repo.
**/system-connections/*.nmconnection

# SSH keys and the like must never end up in the tree.
*.pem
*_ed25519
*_ed25519.pub
*_rsa
*_rsa.pub
id_*

# Local editor / OS junk.
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Re-include CLAUDE.md (it's globally ignored on this machine but is
# part of this project's documentation).
!CLAUDE.md
